column10: - 2 x Curse of the Snake's Eyes `-2 to roll Heros effect`
- 1 x Suspiciously Shiny Coin `Discard a card on successful Hero effect`
- 1 x Sealing Key `Cannot use Hero's effect`
- 2 x Particularly Rusty Coin `Draw a card on unsuccessful hero roll`
- 2 x Really Big Ring `+2 to use Hero's effect`
- 1 x Decoy Doll `Sacrifice item instead of hero`
